{"tid":660040,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格再造浮誇恥辱紀錄！英乙都沒有如此爛...","createTime":"2018-05-10T10:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T09:49:18.000Z","uid":20634,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"73f03043b2a7a8b19f61732fe2e7b962890820ff","tid":660040,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"　　5月10日淩晨的英超比賽中，阿仙奴作客1-3不敵李斯特城，遭遇英超作客7連敗。<br />\n<br />\n　　今場失利後，阿仙奴遭遇作客7連敗，2018年作客全敗，是英格蘭各級別聯賽中唯一作客沒能拿分的球隊。上一次遭遇作客7連敗還是在1966年。<br />\n<br />\n　　今場比賽是李斯特城1994年11月以來首次在聯賽中擊敗阿仙奴，當時兵工廠的主教練還不是雲格。兩年前李斯特城奇蹟般奪冠的那個賽季，他們遭遇阿仙奴主作客雙殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/05/10/d/d63afeb82fbb225d99e8496b2e034c0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2Fd%2Fd63afeb82fbb225d99e8496b2e034c0e.jpg&h=d5556155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc41bebc3873d16e53414adb9ad57013ed8ea36c","tid":660040,"uid":171754,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92331c105920c1e7ec5f7ab0f85de04fd6c79d66","tid":660040,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8f766c06ae5a992498d518352064300e763069a","tid":660040,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc41bebc3873d16e53414adb9ad57013ed8ea36c","tid":660040,"uid":171754,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"係 擺明玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbc421f7630c8ed005267496328a0f08cd2f867","tid":660040,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"臨走都要玩野"},{"pid":"29e206311e80feb87ea8a23b523912aa173f1399","tid":660040,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"1966<